
To build OSv
============

1) build the specially patched libunwind
   -------------------------------------

    cd ../libunwind
    autoreconf -a
    sh config.sh
    make
    cp ./src/.libs/libunwind.a ../osv/
    cd ../osv


2) build osv
   ---------

    make

To run OSv
==========

1) start the binary in qemu
   ------------------------

    sh scripts/run.sh

2) connect a debugger
   ---------------------

    c-a c
    (qemu) gdbserver

    In another terminal:

    # gdb build/debug/loader.elf
    (gdb) connect
    (gdb) bt
